collection_examples

collection_examples.Rd

This is a small data frame of species information for use with the shipping/transferal notes as well as with the label makers.

Usage

collection_examples

Format

A data frame with some collections which will one day be shipped.

Details

this data frame is derived from collections in 2023, which have been cleaned with the BarnebyLives pipeline
